Because of that test, we ended up using DC motors to power our vehicles. On Initiation, we pitted our vehicle against 4 other pledge groups. Although we were doing well in the beginning, an evil gust blew our second stage vehicle off course and away from the target zone :(
We ended up with second place instead. Regardless, the pledge project was really fun and definitely a memorable milestone in my college career.


